ass=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">想問各位巴打明明我份試用期嘅約係講明3個月，但依家已經就黎5個月，法律上係咪應該要簽過份新嘅約？</span><br />\nSor for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n後記：<br />\n呢間公司仲有一個制度係勤工獎，聽落正路呀，不過係由我份糧扣$1k用黎做勤工，一遲到請假早退就扣你$1k，仲要係一分鐘都唔可以遲，一啲buffer time都冇，未返過啲工有呢啲咁閪嘅制度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T04:45:26.000Z","msg":"ST John?荃灣 天水圍都有個間？"},{"pid":"457388e62d4b3b2092ba398dba3cc385ec4d74af","tid":1940676,"uid":24943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58bf57c05e08544406d1496d8ce44a46743a6232","tid":1940676,"uid":73340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"897a593334e7d499bd63495153bdd5ac3c721dd2","tid":1940676,"uid":24943,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"7efcd7f2ad96440b2f1a32d5c7e22604356fdff4","tid":1940676,"uid":238920,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T03:16:27.000Z","msg":"一遲到請假早退就扣你$1k<br />\n<br />\n即係你張約係人工寫10000,實質俾9000,如果冇遲到請假早退就俾10000?<br />\n係如係張約寫係俾10000:<br />\n如果遲到早退一分鐘就扣1000,已經犯左法<br />\n如果請假係當日冇錢再加扣1000蚊,已經犯左法"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T04:41:49.000Z","msg":"張約嘅salary 寫9000，但有個appendix寫1000係勤工<br />\n當初協商係10000<br />\n勤工呢樣野唔緊要，但遲到俾返5分鐘buffer time都好應該啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老實講一個月當有20日返工，我19日都早15分鐘返到，得1日遲左2分鐘，都要計我遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2-3個月都係咁嘅情況"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T04:45:19.000Z","msg":"規矩係咁<br />\n俾你係人情唔俾係道理<br />\n初入社會未熟玩法<br />\n樓主有怒氣係非常正常"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T04:49:25.000Z","msg":"以前返intern都有buffer time<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8de7cbb7ef7635c2962ee264ffd7934eb0ad9666","tid":1940676,"uid":257990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04088dd8f85caf9f9658e5b697bcb426b6b095ab","tid":1940676,"uid":24943,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dfe65a3e729